%h1{class: "mt-4 font-messiri text-center text-2xl tracking-tight sm:text-3xl font-medium uppercase text-red-600"}
  Раді вам запропонувати наші послуги
.mx-auto.p-5.sm:p-10.md:p-16
  .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-3.sm:grid-cols-2.xl:grid-cols-4.gap-10
    - @services.each do |service|
      %a{class: "shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-red-300", href: service_path(service)}
        .border-r.border-b.border-l.border-gray-400.lg:border-t.lg:border-gray-400.bg-white.rounded-b.lg:rounded-b-none.lg:rounded-r.flex.flex-col.justify-between.leading-normal
          - if service.image.attached?
            = image_tag(service.image, class: "w-full h-[150px] sm:w-full sm:h-[200px] transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer filter grayscale-[50%] hover:grayscale-0", alt: service.title)
          - else
            = image_tag("favicon.png", class: "w-full h-[150px] sm:h-[200px] transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer filter grayscale-[50%] hover:grayscale-0", alt: service.title)
          %div{class: "p-4 pt-2 h-auto md:h-64 lg:h-64 xl:h-56"}
            .mb-8
              %p.text-gray-900.font-bold.text-lg.mb-2.hover:text-indigo-600.inline-block
                = service.title
              %p.text-gray-700.text-sm.text-ellipsis
                = service.description
          %div{class: "pe-2 pb-2 text-red-600 w-full flex justify-end items-end"}
            %div{class: "pe-2 sm:pe-4 w-full sm:w-2/3 border-t-2 border-red-300 text-end"}
